signature_matches.name: packed with Mpress
signature_matches.description: anti-analysis/packer/mpress
signature_matches.rule_src:
rule:
  meta:
    name: packed with Mpress
    namespace: anti-analysis/packer/mpress
    authors:
      - william.ballenthin@mandiant.com
    scopes:
      static: file
      dynamic: file
    att&ck:
      - Defense Evasion::Obfuscated Files or Information::Software Packing [T1027.002]
    mbc:
      - Anti-Static Analysis::Software Packing [F0001]
    references:
      - https://www.hexacorn.com/blog/2016/12/15/pe-section-names-re-visited/
  features:
    - or:
      - section: .MPRESS1
      - section: .MPRESS2

signature_matches.name: reference anti-VM strings targeting Qemu
signature_matches.description: anti-analysis/anti-vm/vm-detection
signature_matches.rule_src:
rule:
  meta:
    name: reference anti-VM strings targeting Qemu
    namespace: anti-analysis/anti-vm/vm-detection
    authors:
      - michael.hunhoff@mandiant.com
    scopes:
      static: file
      dynamic: file
    att&ck:
      - Defense Evasion::Virtualization/Sandbox Evasion::System Checks [T1497.001]
    mbc:
      - Anti-Behavioral Analysis::Virtual Machine Detection [B0009]
    references:
      - https://github.com/LordNoteworthy/al-khaser/blob/master/al-khaser/AntiVM/Qemu.cpp
    examples:
      - al-khaser_x86.exe_
  features:
    - or:
      - string: /Qemu/i
      - string: /qemu-ga\.exe/i
      - string: /BOCHS/i
      - string: /^BXPC/i
